videos.description: Isaiah Jackson connects with Nate Watson at the rim for a big jam for the Friars.
videos.headline: Watson goes up to slam oop with 2 hands

videos.description: Jamorko Pickett cuts to the rim and finishes with a huge slam over Providence.
videos.headline: Pickett gets up high for one-handed slam

videos.description: Alpha Diallo runs the floor and finishes with a two-handed jam on a Providence fast break.
videos.headline: Diallo goes strong to the rim for 2-handed finish

videos.description: Alpha Diallo gives Providence a 71-70 lead with a corner 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Diallo comes up big with go-ahead 3

videos.description: Mac McClung sends the game against Providence into overtime with a long buzzer-beating 3-pointer.
videos.headline: McClung throws up ridiculous shot at buzzer to force OT

videos.description: Alpha Diallo beats the shot clock to give Providence a 84-80 lead late in overtime.
videos.headline: Diallo drills another clutch 3, this time in OT

videos.description: Georgetown's Isaiah Jackson answers Providence with a long 3-pointer to force double overtime.
videos.headline: Jackson nails a deep 3 to force double OT
